text: Hi! How are you today?
Doing fine.  How are you?
I am doing alright! I would like to talk to you about a charity, do you donate at all?
I do. I have a few local charities I like.
that is great. Have you heard of Save the Children?
Only generally. What do they do specifically?
They help raise funds to ensure children's rights to health, education, safety, etc. around the world
Rights or actual access?
actual access. They have been helping children suffering in war-torn areas, for example
There are enough of those areas.
exactly, and it is not fair for these children to suffer
Right. What's your proposition?
I encourage you to donate some or all of your bonus today to help save these children
Let's settle on $.15 for today.
every little bit helps! .15 is great!
You bet. Hope they get to use it right away.
yes the researchers ensure that the money gets to the children
Excellent.  They must have a pretty decent charity rating.
They do what they can to help the children
Anything else I can do for you?
